results.title: Haiti severely damaged by earthquake
results.description: On this day in 2010, a magnitude-7.0 earthquake devastated Haiti, especially Port-au-Prince, killing more than 200,000 people and leaving more than 1,000,000 homeless and touching off a massive international relief effort

results.title: U.S. Deep Impact Probe Strikes Tempel 1 Comet
results.description: The U.S. space probe Deep Impact was launched, and in July it shot a 370-kg (810-pound) mass into the nucleus of the comet Tempel 1 in order to study its cometary structure
